{"tid":1243351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要忘記烈士","createTime":"2019-06-19T12:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T13:38:32.000Z","uid":105615,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad5f0e1a8108e92f5c38a08aff7bdf351f637c6","tid":1243351,"uid":105615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"朋友轉發左烈士fb比我<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marco.leung.5855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarco.leung.5855&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=334a052b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marco.leung.5855</a><br />\n<br />\n我碌左幾張相泥睇 <br />\n相裡面既烈士係笑得好開心<br />\n我睇左幾張已經冇辦法睇落去 <br />\n<br />\n到底政府要令到烈士幾絕望先放棄生命<br />\n但呢個政府都冇理過我地<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n6.21請大家一定要出泥<br />\n6.22烈士頭七  大家都一定要到 <br />\n比烈士知道我地永遠都記得佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7612dc3b265bae4866d677cfe4957e243b45c763","tid":1243351,"uid":259423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:06:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b62a6c5b6386752646c7c59a6eb3b78edad04590","tid":1243351,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"絕對 唔會 忘記"},{"pid":"9134da7744853f7258f197863809596f99370605","tid":1243351,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"烈士最後幾個post 係連續貼"},{"pid":"b1c110f801b694f71b504df9a4c257904857c5a9","tid":1243351,"uid":246970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1c7f5c952ae455da1b2c3a79d65f3a484421f4","tid":1243351,"uid":168096,"like":0,"